
=========================
= 		INSTALL			=
=========================
   +
   |
   |
   +{1}+------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------+
   |   |                                                                                                                  |
   |   |   Run a standard shell from GAIA source directory                                                                |
   |   |                                                                                                                  |
   |   |   +-----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------+        |
   |   |   +   [user@localhost]$ cat script/sh/template/GAIA.bashrc >> ~/.bashrc && source ~/.bashrc             +        |
   |   |   +-----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------+        |
   |   |                                                                                                                  |
   |   +------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------+
   |
   +{2}+------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------+
   |   |                                                                                                                  |
   |   |   list all available LABSIM software ecosystem                                                                   |
   |   |                                                                                                                  |
   |   |   +-----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------+        |
   |   |   +   [user@localhost]$ gaia-ecosystem --list-all                                                       +        |
   |   |   +-----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------+        |
   |   |                                                                                                                  |
   |   +------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------+
   |
   +{3}+------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------+
   |   |                                                                                                                  |
   |   |   then, simply deploy                                                                                            |
   |   |                                                                                                                  |
   |   |   +-----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------+        |
   |   |   +   [user@localhost]$ gaia-deploy --ecosystem <your_ecosystem_version>                                +        |
   |   |   +-----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------+        |
   |   |                                                                                                                  |
   |   +------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------+
   |
   +{4}+------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------+
   |   |                                                                                                                  |
   |   |   finally, check installed config                                                                                |
   |   |                                                                                                                  |
   |   |   +-----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------+        |
   |   |   +   [user@localhost]$ gaia-check                                                                      +        |
   |   |   +-----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------+        |
   |   |                                                                                                                  |
   |   +------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------+
   |
   +